==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
A quote from a poem by [[wikipedia:Du_Fu|Du Fu (杜甫)]].

Literally: Have read more than 10,000 scrolls.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dú shū pò wàn juàn

===Idiom===
'''[[讀書]][[破]][[萬]][[卷]]'''

# Describes someone who is well-read.

#: '''''讀書破萬卷'''，[[下筆如有神]]。''

===Alternate forms===
[[读书破万卷]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

